<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-10-1333 </DOCNO><TEXT>In view of the 70th anniversary of the discovery of the General Theoryof Relativity, an analysis was made of the special and general theories.The basic postulates, their consequences in the formulation of the theories,the main results, some aspects related to the experimental verificationand its applications are presented, as are some elements of the mathematicalformalism of the theories, to facilitate the logical interrelationshipsbetween its results and consequences. 48 refs.</TEXT></DOC>